<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>My Heart Still Chooses You 💗🥺</title>

<style>
  body {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    text-align: center;
    font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #ffc0cb, #ff9eb5, #ff6f91);
    color: white;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  h1 {
    margin-top: 70px;
    font-size: 36px;
  }

  p {
    font-size: 18px;
    width: 75%;
    margin: auto;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  button {
    padding: 12px 25px;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 25px;
    font-size: 16px;
    cursor: pointer;
    position: relative;
  }

  #yesBtn {
    background: white;
    color: #ff4d6d;
    margin: 15px;
  }

  #noBtn {
    background: #ff4d6d;
    color: white;
    position: absolute;
  }

  #response {
    margin-top: 20px;
    font-size: 20px;
  }

  img {
    width: 200px;
    margin-top: 20px;
    border-radius: 20px;
  }

  a {
    color: white;
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .heart {
    position: absolute;
    animation: float 6s linear infinite;
  }

  @keyframes float {
    0% {transform: translateY(100vh);}
    100% {transform: translateY(-10vh);}
  }
</style>
</head>

<body>

<h1>My Heart Still Finds You 💗🥺</h1>

<p>
I tried to move on… but my heart said no 💭💔  
I tried to forget… but memories won’t let go 🌙😔  
<br><br>
I miss you more than words can show 💞💫  
In every high… in every low 🌸💭  
<br><br>
Your smile 😊 stays in my mind  
Your voice 🎶… one of a kind 💗✨  
<br><br>
Maybe I wasn’t perfect… I know that’s true 😔💔  
But everything I felt… was real for you 💘💌  
<br><br>
So here I am… soft and true 🥺💞  
Still choosing me… still choosing you 💗✨  
<br><br>
Can we try again? 💖🌙  
</p>

<br>

<button id="yesBtn" onclick="yesClicked()">Yes 💖😊</button>
<button id="noBtn" onmouseover="moveButton()">No 😢💔</button>

<div id="response"></div>

<br>

<p>
🎶 <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1nJ2b4RrK3Q" target="_blank">
Play our song — Aje 💗🎧
</a>
</p>

<script>
let noCount = 0;

function yesClicked() {
  document.getElementById("response").innerHTML =
  "You just made my heart smile again 😭💗✨<br><br>" +
  "<img src='https://media.giphy.com/media/l0MYt5jPR6QX5pnqM/giphy.gif'><br><br>" +
  "I promise you… you won’t regret this 💖😊<br>" +
  "I’ll love you softer, better, and realer this time 💞🌸";
}

function moveButton() {
  let btn = document.getElementById("noBtn");
  let x = Math.random() * (window.innerWidth - 100);
  let y = Math.random() * (window.innerHeight - 50);

  btn.style.left = x + "px";
  btn.style.top = y + "px";

  noCount++;

  if (noCount === 2) {
    document.getElementById("response").innerHTML =
    "Are you sure? 🥺💔<br>Maybe think again… please? 💭💗";
  } 
  else if (noCount === 4) {
    document.getElementById("response").innerHTML =
    "Are you really really sure? 😔💔<br>My heart is still here waiting 💞🥺";
  } 
  else if (noCount > 6) {
    document.getElementById("response").innerHTML =
    "Don’t break my heart again… please 💔😢<br>" +
    "That would make me so sad… so lost… 🌧️💭<br>" +
    "and honestly… a little broken inside 😔💔";
  }
}

// floating hearts
for (let i = 0; i < 30; i++) {
  let heart = document.createElement("div");
  heart.className = "heart";
  heart.innerHTML = "💗";
  heart.style.left = Math.random() * 100 + "vw";
  heart.style.fontSize = Math.random() * 20 + 15 + "px";
  heart.style.animationDuration = (Math.random() * 3 + 3) + "s";
  document.body.appendChild(heart);
}
</script>

</body>
</html>
